Description: system metrics collection agent for AI Dashboard
 Collects CPU, memory, disk, network, and GPU telemetry from a host and sends
 samples to an AI Dashboard backend.
 .
 The service supports both root/system installations and regular-user runs:
 root defaults to /etc and /var/lib state paths, while non-root defaults to
 per-user config/state under ~/.config and ~/.local/share.
